{"id":7190,"date":"2023-07-18T13:10:08","date_gmt":"2023-07-18T17:10:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/animalsevent.test\/?p=7190"},"modified":"2023-10-02T23:14:02","modified_gmt":"2023-10-03T03:14:02","slug":"hedgehog-wheels","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/animalsevent.test\/hedgehog-wheels\/","title":{"rendered":"The Ultimate Guide to Hedgehog Wheels: Keeping Your Prickly Friend Active and Happy"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>As an animal expert with years of experience in hedgehog care, I've come to realize the importance of providing these adorable creatures with the right tools and equipment to lead a healthy and fulfilling life. One such essential item for hedgehogs is the hedgehog wheel. In this comprehensive guide, we will delve into the world of hedgehog wheels, exploring their various aspects, benefits, and potential challenges. So, let's roll into the exciting world of hedgehog wheels!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><style>.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn{margin-top:1em;}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .kt-btn-wrap:nth-child(2), .kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .wp-block-kadence-singlebtn:nth-of-type(2){display:none;}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-column{max-height:174px;overflow-y:hidden;-webkit-mask-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, black 50%, transparent 100%);mask-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, black 50%, transparent 100%);}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46.kb-smc-open > .wp-block-kadence-column{max-height:none;-webkit-mask-image:none;mask-image:none;}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46.kb-smc-open > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .kt-btn-wrap:nth-child(1), .kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46.kb-smc-open > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .wp-block-kadence-single